            "text": "{\"code\":0,\"data\":{\"records\":[{\"id\":\"16579711\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-05-29 06:01:53\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-05-29 06:01:53\",\"createUser\":\"\",\"updateUser\":\"\",\"cid\":\"1633\",\"comno\":\"A01\",\"messageCode\":\"SMS2026052800001\",\"topic\":\"20260528系统更新\",\"content\":\"<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">晚上好，</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">伙伴们：</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\\\"text-indent:37px\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">你</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">们</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">好，周四晚上（</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">202</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px\\\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">-</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px\\\">05</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">-</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">28</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">）</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">20</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">：</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px\\\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">0 &nbsp;</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">我们更新内容如下</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">APP</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">端</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">：</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">百易</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">AI</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">新增扫车牌，车架，拍照出入库等功能</span></span></p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950424249039399.png\\\" style=\\\"\\\"/><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950424337019406.png\\\"/><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950424401047071.png\\\"/></p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950438346064653.png\\\" title=\\\"图片4.png\\\" alt=\\\"图片4.png\\\" width=\\\"321\\\" height=\\\"695\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 321px; height: 695px;\\\"/><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950708782059816.png\\\" title=\\\"图片5.png\\\" alt=\\\"图片5.png\\\" width=\\\"321\\\" height=\\\"695\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px; width: 321px; height: 695px;\\\"/><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950656747083758.png\\\" title=\\\"图片6.png\\\" alt=\\\"图片6.png\\\" width=\\\"321\\\" height=\\\"695\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 321px; height: 695px;\\\"/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">APP<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">进店管理，已开单状态的进店车辆列表，在客户经理 右边 增加接待</span></span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">人</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">APP<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">工单管理</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">--</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">已检查和未检查需要分开权限控制，可以设置已检查不给查看</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">APP维修开单<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">服务项目选择，按照选择的顺序进行提取</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">APP<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">维修工单配件明细，添加一个唯一码的展示</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">电脑端：</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">电子健康档案选择自动上传时，可以选择自动上传的业务类型</span></span></p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950772205014376.png\\\" title=\\\"图片7.png\\\" alt=\\\"图片7.png\\\" width=\\\"1100\\\" height=\\\"380\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 1100px; height: 380px;\\\"/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">AI</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">营销 推送到微信群 由拉群员工 改为 按群名称 和 群</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">ID </span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">对应进行推送</span></span></p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950836446094157.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"图片8.png\\\"/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">领料出库和销售出库，出库查询页面加可以修改数量列表</span></p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950859488037344.png\\\" title=\\\"图片9.png\\\" alt=\\\"图片9.png\\\" width=\\\"1100\\\" height=\\\"526\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 1100px; height: 526px;\\\"/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">领料出库单，审核后，库存可售数展示库存扣减当前单据数量后库存数据；</span></p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950898284067134.png\\\" title=\\\"图片10.png\\\" alt=\\\"图片10.png\\\" width=\\\"1100\\\" height=\\\"532\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 1100px; height: 532px;\\\"/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">维修分析页面添加按保险公司分类查询</span></span></p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950922988093923.png\\\" title=\\\"图片11.png\\\" alt=\\\"图片11.png\\\" width=\\\"1100\\\" height=\\\"516\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 1100px; height: 516px;\\\"/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">6.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">领料出库，进店时间，默认改成</span> &nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">最近一个月时间；</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">7.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">销售出库导入数据相同配件，不同数量和销售价，按照导入表格数据区分；</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">8.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">维修历史查询添加实收金额字段查询，可以匹配大于和等于</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">9.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">车辆档案展示的维修金额与工单时候金额不相符</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">10.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">维修查询，维修历史导出，</span></span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">添加</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">设置自定义导出字段，</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">11.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">商品属性导出列表，添加上架状态参数</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">12.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">三包索赔</span>/<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">厂家索赔开单领用配件，配件索赔价格，批量修改时添加一键替换为成本价的按钮功能，配件金额需联动</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">13.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">进店车辆列表需要添加一个是否开工单的查询条件</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">14.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">经营参谋，维修历史列表底部，添加维修历史合计</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">15.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">维修查询界面，</span></span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">结算、收银、出厂添加查看合计</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">16.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">储值卡销售历史中添加其他支付明细参数展示</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">17.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">库存</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">查询条件，仓库增加多选</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">18.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">经营参谋</span>--<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">服务查询</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">--</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">三包查询</span></span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">增加班组和主修员</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">19.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">服务查询，三包查询，列表和导出，需要添加一下所有账类成本金额字段</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">20.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">服务查询保险理赔列表展示，配件成本，实收成本，配件利润，实收利润，不含税成本金额字段</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">百易云修</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">祝大家生意兴隆！</span></strong></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>\",\"acceptType\":0,\"sendTime\":\"2026-05-29 06:01:53\",\"fromUserCode\":\"\",\"fromUserName\":\"\",\"acceptCode\":\"A01YG20240824001\",\"acceptName\":\"张三\",\"acceptPhone\":\"13759223368\",\"sendStatus\":1,\"status\":1,\"remarks\":\"未找到当前员工的连接信息\",\"sendType\":2,\"businessType\":0,\"businessCode\":\"\",\"smsContent\":\"\",\"voiceContent\":\"\",\"spare1\":\"\"},{\"id\":\"16535415\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-05-27 17:46:02\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-05-27 17:46:02\",\"createUser\":\"张三\",\"updateUser\":\"张三\",\"cid\":\"1633\",\"comno\":\"A01\",\