            "text": "{\"code\":0,\"data\":{\"records\":[{\"id\":\"2005\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-05-28 14:49:02\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-05-29 06:06:23\",\"createUser\":\"1\",\"updateUser\":\"1\",\"createIp\":\"113.80.130.214\",\"updateIp\":\"113.80.130.214\",\"messageCode\":\"SMS2026052800001\",\"topic\":\"20260528系统更新\",\"content\":\"<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">晚上好，</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">伙伴们：</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\\\"text-indent:37px\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">你</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">们</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">好，周四晚上（</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">202</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px\\\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">-</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px\\\">05</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">-</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">28</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">）</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">20</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">：</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px\\\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">0 &nbsp;</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">我们更新内容如下</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">APP</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">端</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">：</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">百易</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">AI</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">新增扫车牌，车架，拍照出入库等功能</span></span></p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950424249039399.png\\\" style=\\\"\\\"/><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950424337019406.png\\\"/><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950424401047071.png\\\"/></p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950438346064653.png\\\" title=\\\"图片4.png\\\" alt=\\\"图片4.png\\\" width=\\\"321\\\" height=\\\"695\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 321px; height: 695px;\\\"/><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950708782059816.png\\\" title=\\\"图片5.png\\\" alt=\\\"图片5.png\\\" width=\\\"321\\\" height=\\\"695\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 14px; width: 321px; height: 695px;\\\"/><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950656747083758.png\\\" title=\\\"图片6.png\\\" alt=\\\"图片6.png\\\" width=\\\"321\\\" height=\\\"695\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 321px; height: 695px;\\\"/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">APP<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">进店管理，已开单状态的进店车辆列表，在客户经理 右边 增加接待</span></span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">人</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">APP<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">工单管理</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">--</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">已检查和未检查需要分开权限控制，可以设置已检查不给查看</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">APP维修开单<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">服务项目选择，按照选择的顺序进行提取</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">APP<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">维修工单配件明细，添加一个唯一码的展示</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">电脑端：</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">电子健康档案选择自动上传时，可以选择自动上传的业务类型</span></span></p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950772205014376.png\\\" title=\\\"图片7.png\\\" alt=\\\"图片7.png\\\" width=\\\"1100\\\" height=\\\"380\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 1100px; height: 380px;\\\"/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">AI</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">营销 推送到微信群 由拉群员工 改为 按群名称 和 群</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">ID </span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">对应进行推送</span></span></p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950836446094157.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"图片8.png\\\"/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">领料出库和销售出库，出库查询页面加可以修改数量列表</span></p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950859488037344.png\\\" title=\\\"图片9.png\\\" alt=\\\"图片9.png\\\" width=\\\"1100\\\" height=\\\"526\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 1100px; height: 526px;\\\"/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">领料出库单，审核后，库存可售数展示库存扣减当前单据数量后库存数据；</span></p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950898284067134.png\\\" title=\\\"图片10.png\\\" alt=\\\"图片10.png\\\" width=\\\"1100\\\" height=\\\"532\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 1100px; height: 532px;\\\"/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">维修分析页面添加按保险公司分类查询</span></span></p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260528/1779950922988093923.png\\\" title=\\\"图片11.png\\\" alt=\\\"图片11.png\\\" width=\\\"1100\\\" height=\\\"516\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 1100px; height: 516px;\\\"/></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">6.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">领料出库，进店时间，默认改成</span> &nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">最近一个月时间；</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">7.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">销售出库导入数据相同配件，不同数量和销售价，按照导入表格数据区分；</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">8.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">维修历史查询添加实收金额字段查询，可以匹配大于和等于</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">9.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">车辆档案展示的维修金额与工单时候金额不相符</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">10.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">维修查询，维修历史导出，</span></span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">添加</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">设置自定义导出字段，</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">11.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">商品属性导出列表，添加上架状态参数</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">12.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">三包索赔</span>/<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">厂家索赔开单领用配件，配件索赔价格，批量修改时添加一键替换为成本价的按钮功能，配件金额需联动</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">13.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">进店车辆列表需要添加一个是否开工单的查询条件</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">14.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">经营参谋，维修历史列表底部，添加维修历史合计</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">15.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">维修查询界面，</span></span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">结算、收银、出厂添加查看合计</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">16.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">储值卡销售历史中添加其他支付明细参数展示</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">17.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">库存</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">查询条件，仓库增加多选</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">18.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">经营参谋</span>--<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">服务查询</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">--</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">三包查询</span></span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">增加班组和主修员</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">19.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">服务查询，三包查询，列表和导出，需要添加一下所有账类成本金额字段</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">20.&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">服务查询保险理赔列表展示，配件成本，实收成本，配件利润，实收利润，不含税成本金额字段</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">百易云修</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">祝大家生意兴隆！</span></strong></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>\",\"type\":1,\"sendTime\":\"2026-05-29 00:00:00\",\"status\":4},{\"id\":\"2004\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-05-14 21:02:05\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-05-15 06:07:51\",\"createUser\":\"1\",\"updateUser\":\"1\",\"createIp\":\"113.87.173.104\",\"updateIp\":\"113.87.173.104\",\"messageCode\":\"SMS2026051400001\",\"topic\":\"20260514系统更新\",\"content\":\"<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">晚上好，</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">伙伴们：</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\\\"text-indent:37px\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">你</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">们</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">好，周四晚上（</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">202</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px\\\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">-</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px\\\">05</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">-</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px\\\">14</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">）</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">20</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">：</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px\\\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">0 &nbsp;</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">我们更新内容如下</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">电脑端：</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">1.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">代办保险添加君子签合同对接</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;<img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260514/1778763592234088977.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\" width=\\\"1380\\\" height=\\\"592\\\" style=\\\"width: 1380px; height: 592px;\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260514/1778763616463017643.png\\\" title=\\\"image.png\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\" width=\\\"1414\\\" height=\\\"550\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 1414px; height: 550px;\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260514/1778763646190012953.png\\\" title=\\\"image.png\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\" style=\\\"float: left; width: 1417px; height: 759px;\\\" width=\\\"1417\\\" height=\\\"759\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260514/1778764093391027154.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260514/1778764103319098373.png\\\" title=\\\"image.png\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\" width=\\\"664\\\" height=\\\"1336\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 664px; height: 1336px;\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">2.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">AI<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">摄像头 &nbsp;预约管理 进店车辆 增加进店车辆 &nbsp;和 消息通知</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><br/></span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">3.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">进店车辆</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">增加</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">离店时间，在店时长，上工位，下工位，工位，</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">在工位时长，业务类型</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\"><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260514/1778763768266067106.png\\\" title=\\\"image.png\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\" width=\\\"1450\\\" height=\\\"650\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 1450px; height: 650px;\\\"/></span></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">4.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">PC<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">端 进店车辆 &nbsp;增加历程： &nbsp;到店日期、上工位时间、工位、下工单时间</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;<img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260514/1778764245216082049.png\\\" title=\\\"image.png\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\" width=\\\"1420\\\" height=\\\"555\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 1420px; height: 555px;\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">5.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">维修管理</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">洗美</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">开工单时</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">当启用了</span>AI<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">摄像头时 开工单后将工单和车辆信息同步到 进店车辆中</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">6.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">PC<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">端 结算状态 出厂状态 &nbsp;&nbsp;增加批量打印</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;<img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260514/1778764003014099698.png\\\" title=\\\"image.png\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\" width=\\\"1418\\\" height=\\\"495\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 1418px; height: 495px;\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">7.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">拓客营销活动，加个设置可以控制是否展示在小程序上面，需要可以设置个别活动不展示小程序上面，只通过分享扫码进</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">8.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">短信</span></span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">和公众号</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">扣储值卡信息，本次消费金额需要调整成（本金</span>+<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">赠送）</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">9.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">经营参谋</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">套餐储值</span> &nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">套餐销售历史增加发票类型和套餐分类二个字段</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;<img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260514/1778764283184065464.png\\\" title=\\\"image.png\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\" width=\\\"1415\\\" height=\\\"597\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 1415px; height: 597px;\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">10.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">库存调价，批量修改时，根据价格关系计算，价格关系设置为空时，不进行计算和替换</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">11.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">应付明细没有导出备注字段，</span></span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">添加</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">自定义设置导出配置功能</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">12.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">PC<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">端 施工单 报价单 和结算单 &nbsp;增加打印 保险公司和定损员</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">13.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">财务查询，收款明细查看合计，</span></span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">展示</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">优惠金额合计</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">14.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">套餐销售历史，网格，查询，导出，需要添加一个套餐类型：油卡</span>/<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">套餐卡</span></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">APP</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">端</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">1.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">APP</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">洗美单加上客户经理显示</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;<img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260514/1778764381172087492.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">2.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">APP</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">销售退货，输入客户名后再输入条件，在客户销售记录里查询</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">3.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">APP &nbsp;</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">增加参数 默认 显示 商机页面</span></span></p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;text-justify:distribute-all-lines\\\"><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;<img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260514/1778764392087078097.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></span></p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;text-justify:distribute-all-lines\\\"><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260514/1778764404375003005.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">4.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">APP </span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">进店车辆</span></span></p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;text-justify:distribute-all-lines\\\"><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;<img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260514/1778764414971068440.png\\\" title=\\\"image.png\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\" width=\\\"664\\\" height=\\\"1736\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 664px; height: 1736px;\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260514/1778764466474617643.png\\\" title=\\\"image.png\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\" width=\\\"664\\\" height=\\\"1236\\\" border=\\\"0\\\" vspace=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"width: 664px; height: 1236px;\\\"/>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">百易云修</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">祝大家生意兴隆！</span></strong></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>\",\"type\":1,\"sendTime\":\"2026-05-15 00:00:00\",\"status\":4},{\"id\":\"2003\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-05-01 10:14:31\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-05-02 06:04:53\",\"createUser\":\"1\",\"updateUser\":\"1\",\"createIp\":\"223.104.79.30\",\"updateIp\":\"223.104.79.30\",\"messageCode\":\"SMS2026050100003\",\"topic\":\"祝大家五一快乐！2026.5.1~3放假\",\"content\":\"<p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260501/1777601658156032380.jpg\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"51放假.jpg\\\" width=\\\"1114\\\" height=\\\"2657\\\" style=\\\"width: 1114px; height: 2657px;\\\"/></p>\",\"type\":2,\"sendTime\":\"2026-05-02 00:00:00\",\"status\":4},{\"id\":\"2000\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-02 22:47:40\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-04-03 06:04:36\",\"createUser\":\"1\",\"updateUser\":\"1\",\"createIp\":\"113.87.184.142\",\"updateIp\":\"113.87.184.142\",\"messageCode\":\"SMS2026040200001\",\"topic\":\"20260402系统更新\",\"content\":\"<p><span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\\\">尊敬的用户：</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\\\">你好，周四晚上（2026-04-02）21：30&nbsp; 我们更新内容如下</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\\\">电脑端：</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\\\">1 会员积分赠送 是否 需要走审核流程，针对4S店等要求比较严格的 走审批流程的 可以开启参数，默认为不审核；</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\\\"><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260402/1775140601780011953.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\\\">2 积分流水表 增加了 积分获得，积分扣减 和 主修员（对应工单的单头的 维修技师）、增加合计栏<br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\\\"><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260402/1775140693833074149.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\\\">3&nbsp;<span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">维修查询里面有项目积分和配件积分字段&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\\\"><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260402/1775140744732071560.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></span></span></p><p><br/></p><p>4&nbsp; 经营参谋&nbsp; 储值套餐 套餐消费明细&nbsp; 增加备注字段&nbsp;</p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260402/1775140986202070620.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></p><p>5 经营参谋 服务查询&nbsp; 增加 汽车电子档案 列表和 评价 ，评价完后上传到重庆电子档案 平台</p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260402/1775141007822053765.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></p><p>6 现金账明细，手动输入的单修改了收入或支出金额，余额不会自动计算</p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260402/1775141132099058449.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></p><p>7 现金账管理，加个打印，显示网格内容和合计</p><p>8 现金账明细，<span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: wrap;\\\">单据号</span>点击可以转原单</p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260402/1775141176110080664.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></p><p>9 领料出库，开单点击领料时，没有需求配件不弹窗选择，直接开领料出库单</p><p><img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260402/1775141219843012214.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\\\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\\\">百易云修</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\\\">祝大家生意兴隆！</span></p><p><span style=\\\"text-wrap-mode: nowrap;\\\"><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><br/></span></span><br/></p>\",\"type\":1,\"sendTime\":\"2026-04-03 00:00:00\",\"status\":4},{\"id\":\"1999\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-03-26 15:12:56\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-03-27 06:06:55\",\"createUser\":\"1\",\"updateUser\":\"1\",\"createIp\":\"223.104.79.107\",\"updateIp\":\"223.104.79.107\",\"messageCode\":\"SMS2026032600001\",\"topic\":\"20260326系统更新\",\"content\":\"<p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">尊敬的用户：</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=\\\"text-indent:37px\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">你</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">好，周四晚上（</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">202</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px\\\">6</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">-</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px\\\">03</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">-</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px\\\">26</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">）</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">20</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">：</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: Calibri;font-size: 19px\\\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">0 &nbsp;</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">我们更新内容如下</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">电脑端：</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">1.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">库存</span></span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">明细修改拆分为改数量，仓库仓位，成本价，销售类价格</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">，</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">商品属性信息按钮</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;<img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260326/1774509077722072586.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">2.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">套餐销售</span> &nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">选择套餐页面</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">增加</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">新建套餐</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">入口</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;<img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260326/1774509089821078563.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">3.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">储值卡销售</span> &nbsp;<span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">选择</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">套餐和</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">选择储值卡</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">在搜索</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">右边</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">增加</span> <span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">新增</span></span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">储</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">值卡</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;<img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260326/1774509100139059523.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">4.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">会员积分反馈，计算规则从需求配件调整为领用配件</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">5.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">PC</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">端 维修管理 </span></span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">添加</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">工单备注和结算备注</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">6.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">预约订单，搜索加</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">‘预约时间’，网格加</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">2</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">个字段‘优惠金额’和‘优惠劵名</span></span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">，</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">导出按钮</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;<img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260326/1774509114253098566.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">7.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">现金账明细，合计里的余额去</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">除</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">8.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">首页按时间查询后，点击在修工单跳转到历史页面，查询</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">对应查询日期数据</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">9.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">现金账明细，加个打印，打印网格里的内容和合计</span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">10.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">轮胎寄存单，需要添加二维码打印的选项</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;<img src=\\\"https://minio.cloud.harsons.cn/bsy/bayicloud/0/ueditor/upload/image/20260326/1774509124010027382.png\\\" title=\\\"\\\" alt=\\\"image.png\\\"/></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">11.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">库存移库，目标仓位超过</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">5</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">位数时，需要重新点击目标仓位输入框才能继续编辑</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">APP</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">端</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">1.</span><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">APP </span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">轮胎寄存和领料 增加 分享</span><span style=\\\"font-family:Calibri\\\">H5</span><span style=\\\"font-family:宋体\\\">和签字确认</span></span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">百易云修</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\\\"font-family: 宋体;font-size: 19px\\\">祝大家生意兴隆！</span></strong></p><p><span style=\\\";font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\\\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>\",\"type\":1,\"sendTime\":\"2026-03-27 00:00:00\",\"status\":4}],\"total\":\"13\",\"size\":\"5\",\"current\":\"1\",\"orders\":[],\"hitCount\":false,\"searchCount\":true,\"pages\":\"3\"},\"msg\":\"ok\",\"path\":null,\"extra\":null,\"timestamp\":\"1780112576673\",\"errorcode\":0,\"error\":null,\"isSuccess\":true,\"isError\":false}"
